title: Grateful Dead Live at Meadowlands Arena on 1983-04-16

description:
Set 1

Minglewood Blues, Tennessee Jed, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Bird Song, My Brother Esau, West L.A. Fadeaway, Maybe You Know, Looks Like Rain-> Touch Of Gray

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider-> Uncle John's Band-> Truckin'-> Drumz-> Black Queen*-> Iko Iko*-> Bob Star-> The Other One-> Black Peter-> One More Saturday Night*, E: Johnny B. Goode*

*w/ Stephen Stills
final/last "Black Queen": 12-10-69

reviews.review_text: NICE Good sound, nice show! Thank you for sharing!

real good time Thanks for posting this. I had a multigeneration audience tape of this 30 years ago that sounded like mud, but the Stephen Stills guest parts were tremendous anyway.
Love the clean board sound!
